@node Main "Kaleido - Documentation"

                              'Kaleido' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" Kaleido " link play} is a game where you try to match 50 kaleidoscopic patterns
of variable sizes and shapes. Each of these patterns were randomly
shuffled, and it's up to you to match them with the original pattern,
which is represented by a small drawing located on the upper right in
the game window.

  Try to solve each of the 50 game patterns in the least amount of moves
possible...

  Have fun!

